title: MTA Elections p1
author: TaylorLCling
pages:
#- Today was an historic Day for Mt. Augusta. We had our first election for mayor and judges the date is 10/27/2016. The historic vote ended in 13 votes for SirGrettir and 13 votes for ShaolinPaladin. Then the people turned to me and a few others who were 
#- eligible yet we didnt vote for numberous reason. These votes were supposed to swing the decision however (arguably because of Grettir's support of new people) That vote also ended with a tie. This unprecedented event demanded a recount. I voted for
#- SirGrettir the first time during the snap vote, I dont know if I will vote the same during the recount but time will tell... 
#- 